\id 1JN Meitei: Roman Script 1st Translation 
\h 1 John 
\toc1 JOHN-NA I-ba Ahanba Chithi 
\toc2 1 John 
\toc3 1 Jn 
\mt1 JOHN-NA 
\mt2 I-ba Ahanba Chithi 
\imt1 Wahoudok 
\im Ahanba John hairiba chithi asi Christtana pokpa matung chahi 50 dagi 100 phaobagi manungda Pakhonchatpa John-na i-rambani. John-na chithi asigi a-iba adu mahakni haina sak taklamde adubu chithi asigi ahanba pandupta mahak Jisuna hinglamba amadi sibadagi hinggatpa adu mitna uhouba misak amani haina utli (1:1-3). I John-da i-ba mawong asiga John-na i-ba Aphaba Pao adugi i-ba mawong adugasu yamna manei. John-na i-ba Aphaba Pao aduga chithi ahum haibadi 1 John, 2 John amadi 3 John hairibasing asi John-na Ephesus-ta leiringeida i-bani haina thajanei. 
\ip John-na chithi asi Christian pumnamakta i-bani, matam aduda “Gnostic” kouba mioi kangbu amana maram oiduna singlupna khudong chadaba thengnariba matamni. Mioising asina Jisudi mapung phana Tengban Mapu oibani adubu ee-tonggi hakchang panba tasengba mioiba ama natte haina thajarammi. Masigi maramgidamak Jisuna hingba uhouba amadi mahakki makhutmakna soklaba (1:1-3) adugi maramda John-na i-bani. Chithi asi, mahakki haraoba mapung phahannaba (1 John 1:4) thajabasingna pap touba thingnanaba (1 John 2:1) thajabasingbu aranba tambibadagi ngakthoknaba (1 John 2:26) amasung thajaba makhoising adu kanbiba phangle haibasi soidrabani hainanaba John-na i-bani (5:13). 
\iot Yaopham Takpa 
\io1 1. Chithi asibu masak takpa amadi masi i-bagi maram ama piba \ior (1:1-4)\ior* 
\io1 2. Tengban Mapudi mangalni amadi Jisuna hinglamba matougumna eikhoinasu hinggadabani haiba adu sugaina takpa \ior (1:5–3:10)\ior* 
\io1 3. Amaga amaga nungsinou haiba yathang adu mahakna eikhoida ningsingba \ior (3:11–5:12)\ior* 
\io1 4. Mahakki chithi adu loisinba \ior (5:13-21)\ior* 
\c 1  
\s1 Hingbagi wa 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 1:1 \xt Jn 1:1\x*Ahoubadagi leiraklaba, hingbagi Wa adugi maramda nakhoida eikhoina i-ri. Eikhoina madu tare, eikhoigi imitna ure; hoi, eikhoina ujare amasung eikhoigi khutna madu sokle.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 1:2 \xt Jn 1:14\x*Hingba adu uhanbire; eikhoina madu ujare amadi madugi maramda eikhoina sakhi pi amasung eikhoida uhanbiba amadi Mapa Ibungoga leiminnaramba lomba naidaba hingba adu eikhoina nakhoida laothok-i.  
\v 3 Nakhoisu eikhoiga tinanaba eikhoina uraba amadi taraba adu nakhoida laothok-i. Eikhoigi tinnaba adudi Mapaga amadi mahakki Machanupa, Jisu Christtagani.  
\v 4 Eikhoigi\f + \fr 1:4 \ft Ariba lairik kharadadi “Nakhoigi” haina yao-i\f* haraoba mapung phahannaba eikhoina masi ijabani. 
\s1 Tengban Mapudi mangalni 
\p  
\v 5 Eikhoina mahakki Machanupadagi taraba amadi nakhoigi naphamda laothoklaba paojel adu asini: Tengban Mapudi mangalni, aduga mangonda amamba amata leite.  
\v 6 Eikhoina Ibungo mahakka tinajei hairaga amambada hinglabadi, eikhoina wahei amadi thabak animakta minamle.  
\v 7 Adubu mahakna mangalda leibagumna eikhoinasu mangalda leirabadi, eikhoi amaga amaga tinnaba phangle, aduga mahakki Machanupa Jisugi eena eikhoibu pap pumnamaktagi sengdokpi. 
\p  
\v 8 Eikhoina eikhoida pap leite hairabadi, eikhoi isa ithanta minamjare amasung achumba adu eikhoida leite.  
\v 9 Adubu eikhoina eikhoigi papsing Tengban Mapuda haidokcharabadi, mahakna mahakki wasak adu ngakkani amadi achumba adu tougani: Ibungo mahakna eikhoigi papsing kokpigani amasung aranba touba pumnamaktagi sengdokpigani.  
\v 10 Eikhoina pap toude hairabadi, eikhoina Ibungo mahakpu minamba oihalle, amasung mahakki wa eikhoida leite. 
\c 2  
\s1 Eikhoibu tengbangbiba Christta 
\p  
\v 1 Eigi nungsiraba angangsa, nakhoina pap toudanaba, eina waramsing asi nakhoigi naphamda i-ri; kanagumbana pap tourabadi, Ipagi maphamda eikhoigidamak wanombiba eikhoigi kanagumba ama leiri, mahak adudi achumba chatpa Jisu Christtani.  
\v 2 Ibungo mahakti eikhoigi papki katthokpiraba usin aduni aduga eikhoigita nattana taibangpan pumbagi papkidaksuni. 
\p  
\v 3 Eikhoina mahakki yathangsing ngaklabadi eikhoina mahakpu khang-i haiba eikhoina khang-i.  
\v 4 Kanagumbana “Eina mahakpu khang-i” hairaga mahakki yathangsing indrabadi mahak minambani, aduga achumba adu mangonda leite.  
\v 5 Adubu kanagumba amana mahakki wa illabadi Tengban Mapubu nungsiba adu makhoida tasengna mapung phaba oihalle. Eikhoina Ibungoda lei haibasi masina sengna khangba ngammi:  
\v 6 Tengban Mapuda lei hairiba mahak aduna Jisuna hinglamba adugumna mahakna hingba tai. 
\s1 Anouba Yathang 
\p  
\v 7 \x - \xo 2:7 \xt Jn 13:34\x*Achanbasa, eina nakhoida anouba yathang ama i-ba natte adubu ahoubadagi nakhoida leiraklaba ariba aduni. Ariba yathang asi nakhoina hannana taraba paojel aduni.  
\v 8 Adum oinamak, eina nakhoida anouba yathang ama i-ri, maramdi masigi achumba asi Christtada u-i amasung nakhoidasu u-i. Maramdi amamba adu houkhre amasung achumba mangal adu nganduna leire. 
\p  
\v 9 Kanagumbana mahak mangalda lei hairaga mahakki machin manaobu tukkacharabadi, mahak houjiksu amambada leiri.  
\v 10 Machin manaobu nungsiba mahak adu mangalda lei amasung mangonda khudi thiningai kari amata leite.  
\v 11 Adubu kanagumba amana machin manaobu tukkacharabadi mahak amambada lei amadi mahakna amambada koichat chatli. Amambana mahakpu mamit tanghanba maramna mahakna kadaida chatlibano haiba khangde. 
\p  
\v 12 Eigi nungsiraba angangsa, Christtagi maramgidamak nakhoigi papsing kokpikhraba maramna eina nakhoida i-ri.  
\v 13 Mapa oibasa, ahoubadagi leiraklaba mahakpu nakhoina khangbagi maramna eina nakhoida i-ri. Naha oibasa, nakhoina Phattaba Mahak adubu ngambagi maramna eina nakhoida i-ri. 
\p  
\v 14 Nungsiraba angangsa, nakhoina Ipa adubu khangbagi maramna eina nakhoida i-ri. Mapa oibasa, ahoubadagi leiraklaba mahakpu nakhoina khangbagi maramna eina nakhoida i-ri. Naha oibasa, nakhoi panggal kalli, amadi Tengban Mapugi wa adu nakhoida lei, amasung nakhoina Phattaba Mahak adubu ngambagi maramna eina nakhoida i-ri. 
\p  
\v 15 Taibangpan nattraga taibangpanda leiriba pot amatabu nungsiganu. Kanagumba mi amana taibangpanbu nungsirabadi, Ipabu nungsiba adu mangonda leite.  
\v 16 Taibangpanda leiriba pumnamak haibadi hakchanggi apamba, mitki apamba amasung punsigi napal asising asi Ipadagi lakpa natte, adubu taibangpandagini.  
\v 17 Taibangpan amasung masigi apamba adu mangsillakli; adubu Tengban Mapugi aningba touba mahak adudi matam pumnamakta hingduna lei. 
\s1 Christtagi Yeknaba 
\p  
\v 18 Eigi nungsiraba angangsa, aroiba pungjani; Christtagi maiyokta leiba mahak adu lakkani haiba nakhoina takhibagumna, houjiksu Christtagi yeknaba mayam ama thorakle. Maram aduna aroiba pungjani haiba eikhoina khangle.  
\v 19 Makhoina eikhoidagi chatthokkhibani adubu tasengbadi makhoi eikhoigi oiramde, maramdi makhoi eikhoigi oiramlabadi, makhoi eikhoiga adum leiramgadabani, adubu makhoina chatthokkhiba aduna makhoi amata eikhoigi natte haibadu phongdokle. 
\p  
\v 20 Adubu nakhoidi Christtana nakhoigi nathakta Thawai Asengba heithabikhrabani, maram aduna nakhoi pumnamak achumba adu khang-i.  
\v 21 Nakhoina achumba adu khangdabagi maramna eina nakhoida i-ba natte, adubu nakhoina achumba adu khangbagi maramna amasung achumba adudagi minamba amata laktaba maramna i-bani. 
\p  
\v 22 Adunadi minamba ngangba adu kanano? Jisubu Christtani haiba yadaba mahak aduni. Mahak adudi Mapa amasung Machanupabu yadaba Christtagi yeknaba mini.  
\v 23 Machanupa adubu yadaba mi khudingmak Mapa adubusu yadabani; Machanupa adubu yaba mi khudingmak Mapa adubusu phang-i. 
\p  
\v 24 Nakhoigidamakti, nakhoina ahoubadagi takhraba adu nakhoida lengdana leihallu. Madu nakhoina tourabadi, nakhoisu Machanupada amasung Mapada lengdana leigani.  
\v 25 Christtana eikhoida pibigani wasakpikhiba adu asini madudi lomba naidaba hingba aduni. 
\p  
\v 26 Nakhoibu lanna lamjingnaba hotnariba makhoising adugi maramda eina nakhoida waramsing asi i-bani.  
\v 27 Nakhoigidamakti, nakhoina Ibungo mangondagi phangkhraba thao noibiraba adu nakhoida lengdana lei, aduna nakhoibu kanagumbana tambibagi mathou tade. Adubu Ibungogi thao noibiba aduna nakhoibu hiram pumnamakki maramda tambi aduga thao noibiba adu thanggeisengbani, sasinnaba minamba natte. Nakhoibu tambikhraba adugumna nakhoi Ibungoda lengdana leiyu. 
\p  
\v 28 Aduna houjikti, eigi nungsiraba angangsa, Ibungona lenglakpa matamda mahakki mangda eikhoina ikaiba leitanaba amasung thouna leinaba Ibungoda lengdana leiyu.  
\v 29 Christtadi achumba chatpani haiba nakhoina khanglabadi, achumba touba khudingmak Ibungodagi pokpani haiba nakhoina khang-i. 
\c 3  
\s1 Tengban Mapugi machasing 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 3:1 \xt Jn 1:12\x*Yeng-u, eikhoibu Tengban Mapugi machasing koubinaba Ipana eikhoigi ithakta kayagi matik nungsibire! Madumak eikhoi oiribani! Taibangpanna eikhoibu khangdabagi maramdi taibangpanna Ibungo mahakpu khangde.  
\v 2 Achanbasa, houjik eikhoi Tengban Mapugi machasingni aduga eikhoi kari oigadage haiba houjik phaoba phongdokpidri. Adubu Christtabu phongdokpiba matamda eikhoi mahak man-gani maramdi mahakna oiribagumna eikhoina mahakpu ugani haiba eikhoina khang-i.  
\v 3 Christtada asa asi leiba mi khudingmakna, Ibungona sengba oibagumna makhoi masabu sengdokchei. 
\p  
\v 4 Pap touba mi khudingna wayel yathangbu thugai; tasengna hairabada, papti wayel yathang thugaibani.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 3:5 \xt Jn 1:29\x*Adubu Christtana eikhoigi pap louthokpinaba Ibungo mahak phongdokpire haiba nakhoina khang-i. Ibungoda pap amata leite.  
\v 6 Ibungonda leiba mi amatana pap touduna leite. Pap touduna leiriba mi amatana Ibungo mahakpu usu-udri amasung khangsu-khangdri. 
\p  
\v 7 Eigi nungsiraba angangsa, mi kana amatana nakhoibu lanna lamjing-han-ganu. Ibungona achumba chatpagumna achumba touriba mahak adu achumba chatpani.  
\v 8 Papki thabak touriba mahak adu Devil-dagini, maramdi Devil-di ahoubadagi houna pap tourakli. Tengban Mapugi machanupa adubu phongdokpibagi maramdi Devil-gi thabak manghannabani. 
\p  
\v 9 Tengban Mapudagi poklaba kana amatana pap touduna leiroi, maramdi Tengban Mapugi maru\f + \fr 3:9 \ft Tengban Mapugi mahousa oiba adumak\f* adu makhoida lei; makhoina pap makha tana touduna leiba ngamde, maramdi makhoi Tengban Mapudagi poklabani.  
\v 10 Matou asumna Tengban Mapugi machasing adu kanano amasung Devil-gi machasing adu kanano haiba eikhoina khang-i: achumba toudaba mahak adu Tengban Mapugi macha natte aduga machin manaobu nungsidaba mahak adusu natte. 
\s1 Amaga amaga nungsinou 
\p  
\v 11 \x - \xo 3:11 \xt Jn 13:34\x*Nakhoina ahoubadagi taraba paojel adu asini: Eikhoi amaga amaga nungsinagadabani.  
\v 12 \x - \xo 3:12 \xt Meihou 4:8\x*Phattaba Mahak adugi oiduna Cain-na manao nupa Abel-bu hatpagumna eikhoi oiroidabani. Karigidamak mahakna manao nupabu hatkhibano? Maramdi mahakna toubasing adu aranba oirammi adubu mahakki manao nupana toubasing adu achumba oirammi. 
\p  
\v 13 Eigi ichil inaosa, taibangpanna nakhoibu tukkacharabadi maduda ngakkanu.  
\v 14 \x - \xo 3:14 \xt Jn 5:24\x*Eikhoidi sibadagi hingbada lanthokle haiba eikhoina khang-i, maramdi eikhoi amaga amaga nungsinei. Nungsidaba mahak adu sibada leiri.  
\v 15 Machin manaobu tukkachaba mahak adu mihatpani, mihatpa mi amatada lomba naidaba hingba leite haiba nakhoina khang-i.  
\v 16 Matou asumna nungsiba asi karino haiba eikhoina khang-i: Jisu Christtana eikhoigidamak mahakki thawai katthokpi. Madu oirabadi, eikhoinasu ichil inaosinggidamak eikhoigi thawai katthokpham thok-i.  
\v 17 Lan thum leiba kanagumba amana mahakki machin manaosinggi awatpa adu uraga makhoigidamak mangonda nungsibiba leitrabadi, karamna Tengban Mapugi nungsiba adu mangonda leibage?  
\v 18 Eigi nungsiraba angangsa, eikhoina waheitana nattraga ngangbatana nungsigumsi, adubu thabakna amasung achumbana nungsisi. 
\s1 Tengban Mapugi mangda thouna phaba 
\p  
\v 19 Matou asumna eikhoi achumba adugini haiba khang-i amasung eikhoigi thammoibu Ibungogi mangda langtaknaba yaodana eikhoibu leihalli.  
\v 20 Eikhoigi thammoina eikhoibu lalhallabadi, Tengban Mapuna eikhoigi thammoidagi henna chao-i amasung Ibungona pumnamak khangbi haiba eikhoina khang-i.  
\v 21 Achanbasa, eikhoigi thammoina eikhoibu lalhandrabadi, Tengban Mapugi mangda eikhoigi thouna phaba lei.  
\v 22 Eikhoina Ibungo mahakki yathang ngakpa amasung mahakki apenba adu touba maramna eikhoigi nijaba makhei eikhoina mangondagi phangjei.  
\v 23 \x - \xo 3:23 \xt Jn 13:34; 15:12,17\x*Mahakki yathang adudi: mahakki Machanupa Jisu Christtagi mingda thajaba amasung Christtana eikhoida yathang pibagumna eikhoi amaga amaga nungsinaba aduni.  
\v 24 Tengban Mapugi yathang ngakpa mahak adu Ibungo mangonda lei amasung Ibungo mahakna mangonda lei. Tengban Mapuna eikhoida pibiba Thawai adugi mapanna Tengban Mapuna eikhoida lei haiba eikhoina khang-i. 
\c 4  
\s1 Achumba Thawai amasung chumdaba thawai 
\p  
\v 1 Achanbasa, thawai khudingmak thajaganu, adubu thawaising adu Tengban Mapudagi lakpra haiba khangnaba chang yeng-u, maramdi wa phongdoksinnaba yamna taibangpanda chatthokkhre.  
\v 2 Masidagi nakhoina Tengban Mapugi Thawai adu khanggani: Jisu Christtana hakchang oina lakle haiba adu chummi haina yajaba thawai khuding adu Tengban Mapudagini.  
\v 3 Adubu Jisubu hakchang oina lakle haiba adu yadaba thawai khudingmak Tengban Mapudagi natte. Madu nakhoina lakkani haina taba Christtabu Yeknaba adugi thawaini aduga houjikmak mahak taibangpan asida leirabani. 
\p  
\v 4 Eigi nungsiraba angangsa, nakhoidi Tengban Mapudagini, aduga nakhoina makhoibu ngamle, maramdi taibangpanda leiba mahak adudagi nakhoigi nungda leiba mahakna henna chao-i.  
\v 5 Wa phongdoksinnaba makhoising adu taibangpanbadagini maram aduna makhoina taibangpan-gi oiba maramda ngang-i aduga taibangpanna makhoina haiba adu tai.  
\v 6 Eikhoi Tengban Mapugini, Tengaban Mapubu khangba misingna eikhoigi wa tai adubu Tengban Mapugi nattaba misingna eikhoigi wa tade. Masidagi eikhoina achumbagi Thawai amasung aranbagi thawai adu khang-i. 
\s1 Tengban Mapudi nungsibani. 
\p  
\v 7 Achanbasa, eikhoi amaga amaga nungsinasi, maramdi nungsibasi Tengban Mapudagi lakpani. Nungsiba mi khudingmak Tengban Mapudagi pokpani amasung Tengban Mapubu khang-i.  
\v 8 Nungsidaba mahak aduna Tengban Mapubu khangde; maramdi Tengban Mapudi nungsibani.  
\v 9 Tengban Mapuna eikhoibu nungsibiba adu asumna utpire madudi mahakna mahakki amatta ngairaba Machanupabu taibangpanda thabire, masi eikhoina mahakki mapanna hingnanabani.  
\v 10 Masini nungsiba haiba adu: eikhoina Tengban Mapubu nungsire haiba natte, adubu Tengban Mapuna eikhoibu nungsibiraduna eikhoigi papkidamak usin-gi irapot oinaba mahakki Machanupabu thabire. 
\p  
\v 11 Achanbasa, Tengban Mapuna eikhoibu asuk nungsibirabadi, eikhoinasu amaga amaga nungsinapham thok-i.  
\v 12 \x - \xo 4:12 \xt Jn 1:18\x*Mi kana amatana Tengban Mapubu ukhidri adubu eikhoina amaga amaga nungsinarabadi, Tengban Mapuna eikhoida lei aduga mahakki nungsiba adu eikhoida mapung phaba oihalle. 
\p  
\v 13 Ibungona eikhoida mahakki Thawai pibiba maramna eikhoina Ibungonda lei amasung Ibungona eikhoida lei haiba eikhoina khang-i.  
\v 14 Mapa aduna mahakki Machanupa adubu taibangpanbagi Kanbiba Mapu oinaba thabirakle haiba adu eikhoina ure amasung eikhoina sakhi pi.  
\v 15 Jisudi Tengban Mapugi Machanupani haiba adu achumbani haina yajaba mi aduda Tengban Mapuna lei amasung mahakna Tengban Mapuda lei.  
\v 16 Tengban Mapuna eikhoibu nungsibiba adu eikhoina khangle amasung thajare. 
\p Tengban Mapudi nungsibani. Kanagumbana nungsibada leirabadi mahak Tengban Mapuda leirabani amasung Tengban Mapuna mangonda lei.  
\v 17 Wayen-gi numitta thouna phana eikhoina leiba yananaba eikhoigi irakta nungsiba adu asumna mapung phahanbire: Taibangpan asida eikhoi Christtagumna oiribani.  
\v 18 Nungsibada akiba leite. Adubu mapung phaba nungsibana akiba tanthok-i, maramdi akibadi cheirak phangbaga mari leinei. Akiba mahak adu nungsibada mapung phade. 
\p  
\v 19 Eikhoina nungsi maramdi Tengban Mapuna eikhoibu hanna nungsibire.  
\v 20 Kanagumba mi amana Tengban Mapubu nungsi hairaga machin manaobu tukkacharabadi, mahak chinthibani. Maramdi uraba machin manaobu nungsidaba mahak aduna udriba Tengban Mapubu nungsiba ngamloi.  
\v 21 Ibungona eikhoida yathang asi pibire: Tengban Mapubu nungsiba mahak aduna mahakki machin manaobusu nungsigadabani. 
\c 5  
\s1 Thajabana taibangpanbabu ngamba 
\p  
\v 1 Jisudi Christtani haina thajaba mi khudingmak Tengban Mapudagi poklabani aduga mapa adubu nungsiba mi khudingna machabusu nungsi.  
\v 2 Eikhoina Tengban Mapubu nungsiba amasung mahakki yathangsing adu ngakllabadi eikhoina Tengban Mapugi machasingbu nungsi haiba khang-i.  
\v 3 \x - \xo 5:3 \xt Jn 14:15\x*Eikhoina Tengban Mapubu nungsiba haibasi mahakki yathangsing inba aduni. Mahakki yathangsingdi eikhoigidamak potlum natte,  
\v 4 maramdi Tengban Mapudagi poklaba mi khudingna taibangpanbabu ngammi. Eikhoina taibangpanbabu ngamba haibasi eikhoigi thajabagi mapannani.  
\v 5 Taibangpanbabu ngamba mahak adu kanano? Jisudi Tengban Mapugi Machanupani haina thajaba mahak adu khaktanani. 
\s1 Jisu Christtagi maramda sakhi 
\p  
\v 6 Ising amasung eegi mapanna lenglakpa Ibungo mahak adu asini, haibadi Jisu Christtani. Mahakna isingtagi mapanna lakpa natte adubu ising amasung eegi mapannani. Sakhi piriba adu Thawai adunani maramdi Thawai adu achumbani.  
\v 7 Sakhi ahum lei:  
\v 8 Thawai, ising amasung eeni; ahum asi amata oina yanei.  
\v 9 Eikhoina mioibagi sakhi lou-i adubu Tengban Mapugi sakhina henna chao-i maramdi mahakki Machanupagi maramda sakhi piriba asi Tengban Mapugi sakhini.  
\v 10 Tengban Mapugi Machanupa adubu thajaba makhoina sakhi asi lou-i. Tengban Mapubu thajadaba makhoina Tengban Mapubu chinthiba oihalli, maramdi Tengban Mapuna Machanupagi maramda sakhi piba adu makhoina thajade.  
\v 11 \x - \xo 5:11 \xt Jn 3:36\x* Sakhi adu asini, Tengban Mapuna eikhoida lomba naidaba hingba pibire, aduga hingba adu mahakki Machanupa aduda lei.  
\v 12 Machanupa adubu phanglaba mahak aduna hingba adu phangle; Tengban Mapugi Machanupa adubu phangdaba mahak aduna hingba adu phangde. 
\s1 Lomba naidaba hingba 
\p  
\v 13 Tengban Mapugi Machanupagi mingda thajaba nakhoida lomba naidaba hingba lei haibasi nakhoina khangnanaba waramsing asi eina nakhoida i-bani.  
\v 14 Tengban Mapugi maphamda changjabada eikhoigi leijaba chetna thajaba adu asini: madudi eikhoina mahakki ningba matung inna karigumba ama eikhoina nijarabadi, mahakna eikhoigi nijaba adu tabi.  
\v 15 Eikhoina nijaba makhei Ibungona tabi haiba eikhoina khanglabadi, eikhoina mahakki maphamdagi nijakhiba adu eikhoina phangle haiba khang-i. 
\p  
\v 16 Kanagumba nahakki machin manao amana siba thok-hanba nattaba pap touba urabadi, nahakna haijabigadabani aduga Tengban Mapuna makhoida hingba pibigani. Eina hairiba asi siba thok-hanba nattaba pap toubasing makhoi adugini. Siba thok-hanba pap lei. Nakhoina madugi maramda haijagadabani haina eina haiba natte.  
\v 17 Aranba touba pumnamak papni adubu siba thok-handaba pap lei. 
\p  
\v 18 Tengban Mapudagi pokkhraba mi kana amatana pap makha tana touduna leite haiba eikhoina khang-i; Tengban Mapugi Machanupa aduna makhoibu ngaksenbi amasung Phattaba Mahak aduna makhoibu sokpa ngamde. 
\p  
\v 19 Eikhoidi Tengban Mapugi machasingni aduga taibangpan pumbadi Phattaba Mahak adugi makhutta lei haiba eikhoina khang-i. 
\p  
\v 20 Eikhoina achumba Tengban Mapu adubu khangnanaba Tengban Mapugi Machanupa adu lengbiraktuna eikhoida wakhal taba pibire haibasu eikhoina khang-i. Tengban Mapugi Machanupa Jisu Christtada leijaduna eikhoina Tengban Mapuda lei. 
\p  
\v 21 Eigi nungsiba angangsa, nakhoi nasabu lai-murtisingdagi lapna leiyu.